Your privacy is important to us. It is Active User Co.,LTD’s policy to respect your privacy right.
Specifically, our service (Weather Widget) we do not store or collect any other of your information. Please note that we ask the location permission in the app just to show your weather data locally on your device, we don’t store or tracking that data. The weather widget might show ads but we don’t track any of your data.
Our app may link to external sites that are not operated by us, for example, external weather sites. Please be aware that we have no control over the content and practices of these sites, and cannot accept responsibility or liability for their respective privacy policies.
You are free to refuse our request for your current location data, with the understanding that we may be unable to provide you with some of your desired services.
Your continued use of our website will be regarded as acceptance of our practices around privacy and personal information. If you have any questions about how we handle user data and personal information, feel free to contact us.
This policy is effective as of
Jul 11, 2021